Sentencas: Yttrium doped zirconia (YSZ) film was deposited on poly-crystalline 10 at.% samaria doped ceria (SDC) and YSZ plate (doped with 8 at.% yttria) by electron beam evaporation deposition.
Titulo: Nanostructure and conductivity study of yttria doped zirconia films deposited on samaria doped ceria

Sentencas: For electrolyte application in solid oxide fuel cells, YSZ can be used with SDC and act as an electron barrier.
Titulo: Nanostructure and conductivity study of yttria doped zirconia films deposited on samaria doped ceria

Sentencas: The conductivity of YSZ and SDC was measured after sintering at 1000 degrees C. Results indicated that YSZ film became columnar structure, and a new layer formed between the YSZ film and SDC, due to the inter-diffusion between zirconium ions and cerium ions.
Titulo: Nanostructure and conductivity study of yttria doped zirconia films deposited on samaria doped ceria
